# Non-Vietnam correspondence from Charles McMaster Eesley.
#
# This folder holds scans of letters and cards Charlie sent or kept that
# fall outside the 1969–1971 Vietnam tour window held in ../vietnam-letters/.
# Examples: pre-Vietnam Marietta College letters (1968), later cards from
# Charlie to Chuck (2000s), other adult-life correspondence.
#
# See drafts/README-vietnam-letters.md for the naming and workflow that the
# Vietnam set uses; this folder mirrors the convention but holds the rest.
